                              {tag}
                            </span>
                          )
                        })}
                      </div>
                    )}
                  </div>
                </div>
              )
            })}
          </div>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-muted-foreground/70 italic px-1">
            Tiers score don't tell the whole story. Plenty of hidden gems await even with a low score, but you will have to search to discover them yourself.{" "}
            <a href={`${BASE}/how-it-works`} class="underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-foreground transition-colors not-italic">How scoring works ↗</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    )}
  </div>
</Layout>
